<?php
$t = array();
$t[1] = 'G&otilde;diya ta tabbata ga Allah, Mai f&atilde;ra halittar sammai da ƙas&atilde;, Mai sanya mal&atilde;\'iku manzanni m&atilde;su fuk&atilde;fukai, bibbiyu, da uku-uku da hurhuɗu. Yan&atilde; ƙ&atilde;r&atilde;war abin da Ya ke so a cikin halittar. Lalle Allah Mai ĩkon yi ne a kan k&otilde;me.';
$t[2] = 'Abin da Allah Ya buɗa wa mut&atilde;ne daga rahama, to, b&atilde;bu mai riƙewa a gare shi, kuma abin da Ya riƙe, to, b&atilde;bu mai saki a gare shi, waninSa, kuma Shĩ ne Mabuw&atilde;yi, Mai hikima.';
$t[3] = 'Y&atilde; kũ mut&atilde;ne! Ku tuna ni\'imar Allah a kanku. Shin, akwai wani mai halitta wanin Allah da zai azurta ku daga sama da, ƙas&atilde;? B&atilde;bu wani abin baut&atilde;wa, f&atilde;ce Shi. To, y&atilde;ya ake karkatar da ku?';
$t[4] = 'Kuma idan sun ƙaryata ka, to, lalle, an ƙaryata waɗansu Manzanni a gab&atilde;ninka, kuma zuwa ga Allah ake mayar da al\'amura.';
$t[5] = 'Y&atilde; kũ mut&atilde;ne! Lalle wa\'adin Allah gaskiya ne, sab&otilde;da haka kada r&atilde;yuwar dũniya ta rũɗar da ku, kuma kada marũɗi ya rũɗe ku game da Allah.';
$t[6] = 'Lalle Shaiɗan maƙiyi ne a gare ku, sai ku riƙe shi maƙiyi. Yan&atilde; kiran ƙungiyarsa kawai ne, d&otilde;min su kasance \'yan sa\'ir.';
$t[7] = 'Waɗanda suka k&atilde;firta suna da az&atilde;ba mai tsanani kuma waɗanda suka yi ĩm&atilde;ni, kuma suka aikata ayyukan ƙwarai, sun&atilde; da wata g&atilde;fara da sakamako mai girma.';
$t[8] = 'Shin to, wanda aka ƙaw&atilde;ta masa aikinsa, har ya gan shi mai kyau (yan&atilde; daidai da waninsa)? Sab&otilde;da haka, lalle, Allah Yan&atilde; ɓatar da wanda Yake so, kuma Yan&atilde; shiryar da wanda Yake so, sab&otilde;da haka kada ranka ya halaka a kansu d&ocirc;min baƙin ciki. Lalle Allah Masani ne ga abin da suke san&atilde;\'antawa.';
$t[9] = 'Kuma Allah ne Ya aika da isk&otilde;ki har su m&otilde;tsar da girgije, sa\'an nan Mu k&otilde;ra shi zuwa ga gari matacce, sa\'an nan Mu r&atilde;yar da ƙas&atilde; game da shi a bayan mutuwarta. Kamar wancan ne T&atilde;shin &iexcl;iy&atilde;ma yake.';
$t[10] = 'Wanda ya kasance yan&atilde; nẽman wata izza, to, Allah ne da izza gab&atilde; ɗaya. zuwa gare Shi magana mai d&atilde;ɗi ke hawa, kuma aiki na ƙwarai Yan&atilde; ɗaukar ta Kuma waɗanda ke yin m&atilde;kircin mũnanan ayyuka, sun&atilde; da wata az&atilde;ba mai tsanani, kuma m&atilde;kircin waɗannan yan&atilde; yin tasgaro.';
$t[11] = 'Kuma Allah ne Ya halitta ku daga turɓ&atilde;ya, sa\'an nan daga ɗigon maniyyi, sa\'an nan Ya sanya ku surkin maza da m&atilde;t&atilde;. Kuma wata mace b&atilde; ta yin ciki, kuma b&atilde; ta haihuwa, f&atilde;ce da saninSa, kuma b&atilde; z&atilde; a r&atilde;yar da wanda ake r&atilde;yarwa ba, kuma b&atilde; z&atilde; a rage tsawon ransa ba f&atilde;ce yan&atilde; a cikin Litt&atilde;fi. Lalle, wancan mai sauki ne ga Allah.';
$t[12] = 'Kuma k&otilde;guna biyu ba su daidaita: Wannan mai ruwan d&atilde;ɗi, mai z&atilde;ƙi, mai sauƙin haɗiya kuma wannan mai ruwan gishiri mai zartsi, kuma daga k&otilde;wane, kun&atilde; cin wani nama s&atilde;bo, kuma kun&atilde; fitar da kawa wadda kuke tufantarta, kuma kan&atilde; ganin jir&atilde;ge a cikinsa sun&atilde; m&atilde;su gud&atilde;na, d&otilde;min ku nẽmo daga falalarSa, kuma ɗamm&atilde;ninku z&atilde; ku dinga g&otilde;dẽwa.';
$t[13] = 'Yan&atilde; shigar da dare a cikin r&atilde;na, kuma Yan&atilde; shigar da r&atilde;na a cikin dare. Kuma Ya h&otilde;re r&atilde;n&atilde; da wat&atilde; k&otilde;wannensu yan&atilde; gud&atilde;na zuwa ga ajali ambatacce Wannan Shĩ ne Allah, Ubangijinku, gare Shi mulki yake, kuma waɗanda kuke kira waninSa b&atilde; su mallakar k&otilde; f&atilde;tar gurtsun dabĩno.';
$t[14] = 'Idan kun kira su, b&atilde; z&atilde; su ji kiranku ba, kuma k&otilde; sun jiya, b&atilde; z&atilde; su karɓa muku ba, kuma a R&atilde;nar &iexcl;iy&atilde;ma z&atilde; su k&atilde;firce wa shirkinku, kuma b&atilde;bu mai b&atilde; ka l&atilde;b&atilde;ri, kamar wanda ya sani.';
$t[15] = 'Y&atilde; kũ mut&atilde;ne! Kũ ne m&atilde;su buk&atilde;ta zuwa ga Allah, kuma Allah, Shĩ ne Mawad&atilde;ci, G&otilde;dadde.';
$t[16] = 'Idan Ya so, zai tafi da ku, kuma Ya zo da wata halitta s&atilde;buwa.';
$t[17] = 'Kuma wancan bai zama mabuw&atilde;yi ba ga Allah.';
$t[18] = 'Kuma wani rai mai ɗaukar nauyi, bai ɗaukar nauyin wani rai. Kuma idan ran da aka nauyaya wa k&atilde;ya ya yi kira (ga wani mataimaki) zuwa ga k&atilde;yansa, b&atilde; z&atilde; a dauki k&otilde;me ba daga gare shi, kuma k&otilde; d&atilde; (wanda ake kiran) y&atilde; kasance makusancin zumunta ne. Kan&atilde; gargaɗi kawai ne ga waɗanda ke tsoron Ubangijinsu a fake, kuma suka tsayar da salla. Kuma wanda ya tsarkake, to, yan&atilde; tsarkaka ne d&otilde;min kansa. Kuma zuwa ga Allah kawai mak&otilde;ma take.';
$t[19] = 'Kuma mak&atilde;ho b&atilde; ya daidaita da mai gani.';
$t[20] = 'Kuma duffai b&atilde; su daidaita, kuma haske b&atilde; ya daidaita.';
$t[21] = 'Kuma inuwa b&atilde; ta daidaita, kuma iskar z&atilde;fi b&atilde; ta daidaita.';
$t[22] = 'Kuma r&atilde;yayyu b&atilde; su daidaita kuma matattu ba su daidaita. Lalle Allah Yan&atilde; jiyar da wa\'azi ga wanda Ya so, kuma ba ka jiyar da waɗanda suke a cikin kaburbura.';
$t[23] = 'Ba ka zama ba f&atilde;ce mai gargaɗi kawai.';
$t[24] = 'Lalle Mũ Mun aike ka da gaskiya, kan&atilde; mai b&atilde;yar da bush&atilde;ra kuma mai gargaɗi. Kuma b&atilde;bu wata al\'umma f&atilde;ce wani mai gargaɗi y&atilde; shũɗe a cikinta.';
$t[25] = 'Kuma idan sun&atilde; ƙaryata ka, to, haƙĩƙa, waɗanda suke a gab&atilde;ninsu sun ƙaryata. Manzanninsu sun jẽ musu da hujj&otilde;ji, kuma da takardu, kuma da Littafi mai haske.';
$t[26] = 'Sa\'an nan Na k&atilde;ma waɗanda suka k&atilde;firta. To, y&atilde;ya musũNa yake?';
$t[27] = 'Ba ka gani ba, lalle Allah Ya saukar da ruwa daga sama? Sai Muka fitar, game da shi,\'y&atilde;\'yan it&atilde;ce m&atilde;su s&atilde;ɓanin launuka kuma daga duwatsu akwai zane-zane, farfaru da j&atilde;j&atilde;ye, m&atilde;su s&atilde;ɓanin launin, da m&atilde;su launin baƙin ƙarfe, baƙ&atilde;ƙe.';
$t[28] = 'Kuma daga mut&atilde;ne da dabb&otilde;bi da bis&atilde;shen gida, m&atilde;su s&atilde;ɓ&atilde;nin launinsu kamar wancan. Malamai kawai ke ts&otilde;ron Allah daga cikin b&atilde;yinSa. Lalle, Allah, Mabuw&atilde;yi ne, Mai g&atilde;fara.';
$t[29] = 'Lalle waɗanda ke kar&atilde;tun Litt&atilde;fin Allah kuma suka tsayar da salla, kuma suka ciyar daga abin da Muka azurta su da shi, a asirce da bayyane, sun&atilde; f&atilde;tan (s&atilde;mun) wani fatauci ne wanda b&atilde; ya yin tasgaro.';
$t[30] = 'D&otilde;min (Allah) zai cika musu sakamakonsu, kuma Ya ƙar&atilde; musu daga falalarSa. Lalle Shi Mai g&atilde;fara ne, Mai g&otilde;diya.';
$t[31] = 'Kuma abin da Muka yi wahayi zuwa gare ka, daga Litt&atilde;fi,';
$t[32] = 'Sa\'an nan Mun g&atilde;dar da Litt&atilde;fin, ga waɗanda Muka z&atilde;ɓa daga b&atilde;yinMu, sa\'an nan daga cikinsu, akwai mai z&atilde;lunci ga kansa, kuma daga cikinsu akwai mai tsakait&atilde;wa, kuma daga cikinsu akwai mai tsẽrẽwa da ayyukan alhẽri da iznin Allah. Waccan ita ce falalar (Allah) mai girma.';
$t[33] = 'Gid&atilde;jen Aljannar zam&atilde; sun&atilde; shigar su. An&atilde; ƙaw&atilde;ce su a cikinsu, da ƙaw&atilde; ta mund&atilde;ye daga zĩn&atilde;riya da lu\'ulu\'u, kuma tuf&atilde;finsu, a cikinsu alharĩni ne.';
$t[34] = 'Kuma suka ce: &quot;Godiya ta tabbata ga Allah Wanda Ya tafiyar da baƙin ciki daga gare mu. Lalle Ubangijinmu, haƙĩƙa Mai gafarane, Mai godiya.&quot;';
$t[35] = '&quot;Wanda Ya saukar da mu a gidan zam&atilde;, daga falalarSa, wata wahala b&atilde; ta sh&atilde;far mu a cikinsa, kuma wata k&atilde;s&atilde;wa b&atilde; ta sh&atilde;far mu a cikinsa.&quot;';
$t[36] = 'Kuma waɗanda suka k&atilde;firta sun&atilde; da wutar Jahannama, b&atilde; a yin hukunci a kansu balle su mutu kuma b&atilde; a sauƙaƙa musu daga az&atilde;barta. Kamar haka Muke s&atilde;ka wa k&otilde;wane mai yawan k&atilde;firci.';
$t[37] = 'Kuma sũ, sun&atilde; harg&otilde;war nẽman &atilde;gaji a cikinta. (Sun&atilde; cẽwa) &quot;Y&atilde; Ubangijinmu! Ka fitar da mu, mu aikata aiki mai kyau, wanin wanda muka kasance mun&atilde; aikat&atilde;wa.&quot; Ashe, kuma, ba Mu r&atilde;yar da ku ba, abin da mai tun&atilde;ni zai iya yin tun&atilde;ni a ciki, kuma mai gargaɗi y&atilde; jẽ muku? To, ku ɗanɗana, sab&otilde;da haka b&atilde;bu wani mataimaki, ga azz&atilde;lumai.';
$t[38] = 'Lalle Allah ne Masanin gaibin sammai da ƙas&atilde;. Lalle Shĩ ne Masani ga abin da yake ainihin zukata.';
$t[39] = 'Shĩ ne Wanda Ya sanya ku m&atilde;su maye wa jun&atilde;, a cikin ƙas&atilde;. To, wanda ya k&atilde;firta, to, k&atilde;fircinsa yan&atilde; a kansa. Kuma k&atilde;fircin k&atilde;firai b&atilde; ya k&atilde;ra musu k&otilde;me f&atilde;ce baƙin jini, kuma k&atilde;fircin k&atilde;firai b&atilde; ya k&atilde;ra musu k&otilde;me face has&atilde;ra.';
$t[40] = 'Ka ce: &quot;Shin, kun ga abũbuwan shirkinku, waɗanda kuke kira, wasun Allah? Ku nũna mini, mẽne ne suka halitta daga ƙas&atilde;? K&otilde; sun&atilde; da t&atilde;rayya ne a cikin sammai? K&otilde; kuma Mun b&atilde; su wani litt&atilde;fi ne sab&otilde;da haka sun&atilde; a kan wata hujja ce daga gare shi? &Atilde;\'a, azz&atilde;lumai b&atilde; su yin wani wa\'adi, s&atilde;shensu zuwa ga s&atilde;she, f&atilde;ce rũɗi.&quot;';
$t[41] = 'Lalle Allah Yan&atilde; riƙe sammai da ƙas&atilde; d&otilde;min kada su gushe. Kuma haƙĩƙa, idan sun gushe, b&atilde;bu wani baicinSa da zai riƙe su. Lalle Shi Y&atilde; kasance Mai haƙuri, Mai g&atilde;fara.';
$t[42] = 'Kuma suka yi rantsuwa da Allah, mafi nauyin rantsuwarsu, &quot;Lalle, idan wani mai gargaɗi ya zo musu tabbas z&atilde; su kasance mafi shiryuwa, daga ɗayan al\'umm&otilde;mi.&quot; To, a l&otilde;kacin da mai gargaɗi ya jẽ musu, bai ƙar&atilde; su da k&otilde;me ba f&atilde;ce gudu.';
$t[43] = 'D&otilde;min nũna girman kai a cikin ƙas&atilde; da m&atilde;kircin cũta. Kuma m&atilde;kirci na cũta b&atilde; ya f&atilde;d&atilde;wa f&atilde;ce a kan mut&atilde;nensa. To shin sun&atilde; jiran (wani abu ne) f&atilde;ce dai hanyar (k&atilde;firan) farko. To, b&atilde; z&atilde; ka s&atilde;mi musanya ba ga hanyar Allah. Kuma b&atilde; z&atilde; ka s&atilde;mi jũyarwa ba ga hanyar Allah.';
$t[44] = 'Ashe, kuma ba su yi tafiya ba, a cikin ƙas&atilde;, d&otilde;min su dũba yadda &atilde;ƙibar waɗannan da suke a gab&atilde;ninsu ta kasance? Alh&atilde;li kuwa sun kasance mafĩfĩta ƙarfi daga gare su? Kuma Allah bai kasance wani abu n&atilde; iya rinj&atilde;yarSa ba, a cikin sammai, kuma haka a cikin kaƙ&atilde;. Lalle Shi ne Ya kasance Masani, Mai ĩkon yi.';
$t[45] = 'Kuma d&atilde; Allah Yan&atilde; k&atilde;ma mut&atilde;ne sab&otilde;da abin da suka aikata, d&atilde; bai bar wata dabba ba a kanta (kas&atilde;). Amma Yan&atilde; jinkirta musu zuwa ga ajalin da aka ambat&atilde;. Sa\'an nan idan ajalinsu ya zo, to, lalle Allah y&atilde; kasance Mai gani ga b&atilde;yinSa.';
?>